Dean Witter sells unit to Banque Indosuez . Dean Witter Reynolds Inc said Sunday it has sold its institutional futures business to Banque Indosuez Belgique SA for undisclosed terms . Banque Indosuez plans to combine the unit with its existing global futures operation , Indosuez Carr Futures Inc , the company said . Laurence Mollner , who was executive vice president and director of Dean Witter ' s institutional futures business since 1985 , is to be president of Indosuez Carr Futures . The sale is expected to close by mid - June , the company said . Dean Witter Reynolds is the securities business of Dean Witter , Discover Co . ( ( - - New York Newsdesk 212 - 859 - 1610 ) ) 
